videos.headline: Thornton makes TD catch look easy
videos.description: Tyquan Thornton has no trouble pulling in the wide-open 29-yard touchdown catch from Charlie Brewer.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Thornton makes TD catch look easy) 19/10/05

videos.headline: Lovett finishes Baylor's drive with a TD
videos.description: John Lovett breaks a tackle to increase Baylor's lead over Kansas State with a 13-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One Play (Lovett finishes Baylor's drive with a TD) 19/10/05

videos.headline: Lovett scores again
videos.description: John Lovett goes untouched for an easy 46-yard Baylor touchdown, his second of the game.
